			<tr>
				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">I'm pleased to announce that Brenlo, SOE's Community Manager, has agreed to a Q&A with the Magician's Tower community.
<br />

<br />
Between now and Friday, June 11th, submit your questions that you would like to ask Brenlo about the coming Omens of War expansion. I will pick the best questions and present them to Brenlo.
<br />

<br />
Questions do not have to be specificaly about Omens of War. They can be about the class in general, or about growing concerns in the community. But the general theme should be about Magicians and how they will fit in with the release of Omens of War.
<br />

<br />
Either email them to me, post here in this thread, or PM me.
